”Alexa, open Lucky Number”

skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: lucky number
des: You will be asked to open one of the three boxes presented. Depends on the boxes choosen, you will be informed if you win or lose. If the box is locked, you will be asked to open one of the other two boxes. If you win, you will be prompted with an inspirational quote for kids.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
